entries.text: Peer over the cliff, and hold up the banner
Place the basin at the statue of the beheading knight
A transposing kiln lies within the belly
Arrows of a giant rain down beside the white birch
The path to the archdragons lies through meditation
To travel the Path of the Dragon, do not ring the great bell
Nothing will remain once the bell has tolled
Extinguish three flames, and open the door to Wolf's Blood
Wear wax before nearing the tome
Bring a doll to be granted passage
Even broken, it still has a use
The path to the archdragons lies through meditation
Yhorm's Machete puts great strain on the arm that wields it
Only a storm can fell a Greatwood
To vanquish a giant, bring the sword that rules storms
It would be wise to turn back and search, if you possess not an Estus Flask
PvP-only feature Do not use outside of PvP purpose
The bonfire will deliver thee to Lothric
To soothe the dark sigil, pillage the Fire Keeper's grave
Even the path to the archdragons shall not escape the Abyss
Please ensure you are on banned servers
<?kgAttackR?>: Regular attack Time consecutive attacks perfectly to regain stamina
<?kgStrongAttackR?> : Strong Attack While charging, perform regular attack to feint
<?kgDash?> : Backstep Locked-on backstep grants brief invulnerability <?kgRun?>＋<?kgDash?> : Roll To dash, lock onto an enemy with light equip load
<?kgAttackL?>: Guard/Powerstance Time block correctly for Perfect Block With two of the same weapon class, perform Powerstance attacks
Rest at bonfire : Replenish Estus Flask
<?kgArts?>: Parry (repel attack) <?kgAttackR?>: Riposte (after a successful parry)

Rest at bonfire: Restore resources and warp
